plot: Alex goes into the asylum to retrieve a key, while Michael makes a sacrifice.

Alex embarks on a dangerous quest to prove himself to their newest ally, subsequently reuniting him with a startling face from the past. Meanwhile, Claire enlists the help of an old friend to halt what she believes is a brewing revolt from the V1's. Finally, Michael makes a sacrifice that will spare the town from destruction as well as preserve his identity but will prevent him from ever being with his new love.
